  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to evaluate if there is an association between platelet inhibition
      and surgery-related bleeding in patients undergoing non-cardiac surgery during dual
      antiplatelet therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
